{
  "stem": "294.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So she really lost contact with her parents and-- and her brothers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we had many friends.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And also, like I said, my parents had also mixed friends-- Polish.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father, in his work, he worked in a-- a hospital which was a Catholic hospital, where Poland-- most of the institutions were Catholic, you know.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He had many friends, and I remember them exactly.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He associated with many friends who were non-Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Vienna.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, I stayed in Lodz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And not knowing what will happen-- but I knew one thing-- that we were not-- our whole group-- we will not go back to Vienna.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because we read in the papers-- we heard the news and everything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We knew what's going on there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, in Vienna, I already experienced the first atrocities of the Germans.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because, when we boarded the train, you know, to go, and the train was still at the station in Vienna, the whole group of SS came on the train, examining people's documents.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they behaved like wild animals-- pushing, shoving.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we showed our Polish passports.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at that time, they still respected the Polish passports.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they left us alone, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we heard of the incidents of them attacking the Jews on the streets in the very first day after their arrival.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because we left two days or three days after their arrival, and they already started all this behavior.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I review this moment, because you said you were a group of Polish students in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "On the university in Vienna, you had some feelings that something is happening to the Jews?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Absolutely not-- absolutely not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- this was-- we knew, because there was a plebiscite in Austria.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't remember when it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
